commit message:
Update AllchanModule.getPostsList method

Due to ololord.js API changes, '/api/lastPosts.json' method is now deprecated.
To get new posts, use '/<boardName>/res/<threadNumber>.json' method. Yep, entire thread is downloaded. This is for the sake of caching.
To check for new posts, use 'api/threadLastPostNumber.json' method.

Update AllchanModule.getNewCaptcha method

Use new ololord.js API.
